r les cellules solaires en silicium.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Feb 2021) 4aEnergy. 7aSCIENCE / Energy.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759820061423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9782759820061.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK